upcoming photo spread in Vogue puts the event--which will take place at the New

girlfriends--Samantha, the sexpot; Charlotte, the sweet naÃƒÆ’Ã‚Â¯f; and Miranda, the

for Carrie. Charlotte still has the unrealized hope of getting pregnant.
